<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Bloodforge Hammer Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Head to Qeynos and visit the Fish's Ale.  Wait for Trumpy Irontoe to leave the bar and kill him.  You will need to do it very quick as you will be attacked by guards and bouncers almost immediately.   <BR>
<BR>
2) Take his head back to Byzar and you will receive the Bloodforge Hammer.</div>
<BR>
<table width=100% cellspacing=10>
<tr><td width=50% bgcolor="#0000AF">
