<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Just a few things I have noticed while getting his head.<BR>
1.  It's better just to wait for him to leave.  You can give him honey meads, but it's bad faction with Guards of qeynos and Merchants of Qeynos.  <BR>
2.  Killing him is fairly simple if you're away from guards.  He conned blue to me at level 8 and put up a pretty good fight, so i'm thinking he's level 7.  You also recieve faction adjustments exactly opposite of those you get for giving him the honey meads<BR>
3.  The head is no drop, so you can't get it from a friend.  <BR>
<BR>
Tellemar<BR>
Level 9 Erudite Cleric <BR>
Tunare Server</font></td></tr></table>
